parameters:
So, Lunaroa seems to have taken a liking to this village... The
village chief is also kind.

I might understand Lunaroa's feelings a little. Maybe because it
reminds me a bit of Hatayaki Village.

\SE[67]I had no choice but to do this... \SE[74]You understand,
don't you...?

The road is completely blocked... I don't think I'll ever be able
to go to the village again.
